{
  "texts": [
    "The initial screening was followed by a full-text screening.",
    "The authors evaluated all potentially eligible papers by reading the titles and abstracts.",
    "Following the full screening process, a total of 59 records were eligible to be included in the review.",
    "The articles deemed eligible for review were then further reviewed independently by two independent authors (MK and SL) using a thematic analysis.",
    "Any discrepancies were discussed and resolved in a consensus meeting.The exclusion of records might have resulted in selection bias."
  ]
}